title: Koffin Kats [Inhumane and Straying from the pack]
description:
first of all im just tired of people putting up awesome bands like koffin kats and not seeding it, so im providing what i can. i wasnt able to get their earlier work (its my fault too, i had many chances to buy it when i went to their shows but just didnt have any money) so stuff like V8 Nightmare and shit like that wont be here but it should be good enough for now...

if anyone has any of their early work and their new album that just came out; i would love to get it!

thx
